ypto asset offerings;</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Crypto asset=
 exchanges;</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Crypto asset lending a=
nd staking products;</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Decentralized=
 finance ("DeFi") platforms;</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Non-f=
ungible tokens ("NFTs"); and</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Stabl=
ecoins.</li></ul></blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Notice that it=
=E2=80=99s all in the Division of Enforcement. As far as I can tell the=C2=
=A0Division of Writing DeFi Rules continues to have roughly zero dedicated =
